    • update

      public void update()
      At first check if machine will not be broken by canWork method in state Working. IF machine will broke than call update on next line worker in chain of responsibility. Otherwise it iterate through list of product for work and work on them. Then is called method for simulate depreciation of machine and generate cost statement for tact. At the end is called update method at next line worker in chain of responsibility.
      Specified by:
      update in interface LineWorker
